i expected somekind of nerf, actually i expected it to be in the form of enhancements for all the other classes (which we have begun to see finally), but i really didnt expect them to touch what has become the class defining skill of the rogue<br>
<br>
i hope all of you rogues with ragebringers will be happy when you're dying left and right, me ill be happy with my 15 dmg 40 delay spear and my bladestopper in my off hand<br>
